name: CancerSNOMED
title: Cancer SNOMED
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of SNOMED-CT codes is intended to capture a patient that has a current or historical diagnosis of any form of cancer (other than basal and squamous cell carcinoma of the skin).),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients with an active or historical diagnosis of any form of cancer (other than basal and squamous cell carcinoma of the skin).),(Inclusion Criteria: SNOMED-CT codes associated with all types of cancer are included in this value set (other than basal and squamous cell carcinoma).),(Exclusion Criteria: SNOMED-CT codes not associated with cancer are excluded from this value set, nor are SNOMED-CT codes for basal cell carcinoma and squamous cell carcinoma.)
